features: Ensured Stability & Long-Lasting: Thanks to the high-density MDF board and well-structured metal frame design, this tall bookshelf can withstand the challenge of long-term use. What's more, the sturdy X-shaped support and anti-tipping straps enhance the security and stability of this bookcase to hold up to 30 pounds per shelf. adjustable feet can keep the unit level on uneven flooring and protect the ground from scratches.

Industrial & Farmhouse Design: Narrow bookshelf combines an arc top and metal frames to emphasize the elegance of its lines and the lightness of its design, The two-tone grey with wood grain finish delivers an industrial feel and creates a farmhouse and rustic vibe, which adds a glamorous aesthetic to your space, this grey bookcase can fit perfectly with almost all other furnishing items.

Plenty of Storage Space: This open bookshelf features five tiers of spacious storage shelving that offer ample space for storing and displaying, large bookcase measures 70.87”x 23.62”x 11.02” (H x L x W) with 12.99” between each tier, which maximizes vertical space for all of your daily needs and easily fits the narrow and corner spaces.

Multi-Functional: This farmhouse bookcase can be used as a bookshelf in the study room, an open display rack of collections in your living room or a storage shelf of spices in the kitchen, it also fits perfectly into the bedroom, home office, bathroom, balcony and so on.

Easy Assembly & Easy to Clean: The corner bookshelf comes with step-by-step illustrated instructions and necessary accessories to help you finish the whole installation effortlessly, the hardware and parts are marked with numbers or letters on each piece for your needs, besides, the surface is smooth and waterproof, just clean it with a damp cloth.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great shelf for narrow spots
reviews.reviewText: This shelf is narrow and it fits perfectly between two doors in my hallways. Assembly was a piece of cake. It’s fairly sturdy and looks stylish. Great value for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Turned out great. Really pleased with the price, the pieces & instructions all organized and easy to put together. Feels sturdy enough and looks so nice. Might get a second one for the other side of my daughter's daybed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Most arched bookcases are on the pricey side, for the price point you really can’t beat it. It was easy to put together though one of the bolts didn’t match up it still took less than 20 minutes. Shelves are a good size and the wood doesn’t look cheap or out of place, it looks more expensive than it is. So that’s always a win. Make your house look bougie but on a budget.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful. Love it!
reviews.reviewText: Easy to gather. I did mine a bit wrong but it still stands firm. Fits-in very well and adds a good touch to my overall interior decoration.🥰🥰🥰

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love this shelf! It’s not as big as I thought it was going to be, but I actually love it! It was super easy to assemble and is pretty sturdy for the price! I would recommend it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to start a little library for my room and found this bookshelf that would give me plenty of space for my books. Since I have taller ceilings, when I first put it together I thought it wasn't tall enough, but it ended up still looking good. Able to fit books, bibles, textbooks, and magazines. It was easy to put together and the arches added some personality to the room. I just need to buy book ends and paper weights :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Structurally sound and great quality!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. The product speaks for itself - truly! From delivery to set up it was all carefully and intentionally placed to be safe and easy. The items were placed in order in which they needed to be set up (amazing!) and the instructions are just fantastic! The lettered stickers were super easy to get off and for that I’m thankful. The material is pretty standard, but the quality of the screws to even the perfect screw holes, it’s great. It took me about 40 minutes to set up (w/ a toddler) so surely you could cut that down to 20-25 minutes. As far as the “x” structure on the back of the shelf, you could definitely go without it. It looks nice both ways but I just went ahead and placed it. During installation, you may think you’re short 2 screws for this step but you’re not. You’ll understand during set up, but just know that all pieces are there and you’ll actually have one extra screw :) I think it’s a beautiful shelf and would 100/10 recommend.
